OL,7,FChris Farrimond, NCA director of
OL,8,Fthreat leadership, said: "Vietnamese
OL,9,Fnationals now make up a large number
OL,10,Fof those we see arriving on small
OL,11,Fboats.J"We allege this group were
OL,12,Fadvertising their crossing services on
OL,13,Fsocial media to encourage others from
OL,14,Ftheir country to make the same
OL,15,Ftreacherous journey.J"The NCA is
OL,16,Fcontinuing our work with partners and
OL,17,Fhas had thousands of social media
OL,18,Fpages and posts advertising organised
OL,19,Fimmigration crime services removed
OL,20,Ffrom platforms."JMr Farrimond added:
OL,21,F"Tackling organised immigration crime
OL,22,Fis a priority for the National Crime
OL,23,FAgency and our investigation continues
OL,24,Fto target people smugglers both in the
OL,25,FUK and overseas at every step of the
OL,26,Froute."
